{"prompt": "Generate a website for a AI startup. The website should be playful and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>InnovateAI</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e52b50; /* Red */\n            --secondary-color: #f08080; /* Light Coral - a softer red */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --hover-color: #ff4500; /* OrangeRed for hover effects */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--brand-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);\n            z-index: 0;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n            animation: pulse 2s infinite;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes pulse {\n            0% { transform: scale(1); }\n            50% { transform: scale(1.05); }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); }\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            position: relative;\n            z-index: 1;\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            padding: 50px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .section h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 250px;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 10px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(229, 43, 80, 0.3); /* Reddish shadow */\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .cta {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .cta h2 {\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--hover-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            transform: scale(1.1);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        /* Simple Animation for Icons */\n        .feature-item i {\n            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;\n        }\n\n        @keyframes float {\n            0% { transform: translateY(0); }\n            50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }\n            100% { transform: translateY(0); }\n        }\n\n        /* Responsive adjustments */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            .features {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: center;\n            }\n            .feature-item {\n                width: 80%;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .section h2, .cta h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            .cta-button {\n                padding: 10px 20px;\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>InnovateAI</h1>\n            <p>Unlocking Tomorrow's Potential, Today!</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>What We Do</h2>\n            <p>We build cutting-edge AI solutions that are not only powerful but also intuitive and fun to use. Imagine a world where AI is your creative partner, not just a tool.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\" style=\"background-color: #fff5f5;\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Superpowers</h2>\n            <div class=\"features\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-robot\"></i>\n                    <h3>Smart Automation</h3>\n                    <p>Let our AI handle the repetitive tasks, so you can focus on what truly matters.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-lightbulb\"></i>\n                    <h3>Creative Generation</h3>\n                    <p>From art to code, our AI sparks innovation and brings your ideas to life.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-chart-line\"></i>\n                    <h3>Data Insights</h3>\n                    <p>Understand your data like never before with our intelligent analytics.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cta\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Ready to Play with the Future?</h2>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Get Started Now!</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2024 InnovateAI. All rights reserved. Let's innovate together!</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Add some simple JavaScript interaction if needed in the future,\n        // for now, the animations are CSS-driven.\n        console.log(\"InnovateAI website loaded!\");\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}